{"tid":494770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞漢旺角行人天橋上吊　扯斷皮帶墮地傷","createTime":"2017-12-10T04:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T06:03:16.000Z","uid":76713,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"55e244601c73491fe873fb55951c04cbd66662c0","tid":494770,"uid":76713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:37:07.000Z","msg":"旺角行人天橋南亞漢高處墮下，重傷昏迷。今晨7時53分，一名年33歲南亞裔男子在旺角道近洗衣街一條行人天穚上高處墮下，跌落在馬路中央，多名途人見狀，懷疑南亞漢遭車撞倒報警求助。救護員到場，發現男子重傷昏迷，身上有酒氣，身體多處骨折，相信由離地6米高行人天橋墮下，救護車將傷者送院急救。 <br />\n<br />\n警方在場調查，在行人天橋發現一條扯斷的皮帶繫着欄杆，相信有人在橋上以皮帶吊頸，惟皮帶承受不起重量被扯斷，南亞漢隨即墮地受傷，警員將案件列作企圖自殺，仍在調查事主尋死原因。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171210/mobile/bkn-20171210081637493-1210_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171210%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171210081637493-1210_00822_001.html&d=uDp64KopOkAOKSOp2j%2FPMQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d454848b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171210/mobile/bkn-20171210081637493-1210_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n依班南亞令治安差左幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03377d6bba911bdae1a2acb7ce012b5accabb12","tid":494770,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:37:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d7f83ff9b388bb5865da5471119621f141a750f","tid":494770,"uid":41846,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:39:05.000Z","msg":"啲南狗醫返都嘥藥費"},{"pid":"bfbcf0401126a0b044c6575e3f7a7ee8aa99f76d","tid":494770,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb74dbfcf631c16289cbb4381b01877c0ff2437","tid":494770,"uid":3302,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:43:16.000Z","msg":"搞到成間醫院都係咖哩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac